title: Attack speed numbers appear in chat.
body:
I was playing in Twisted Treeline with Soraka and when I auto attacked any enemy champion some numbers appeared in the chat. I attach a screenshot.

PD: Yes, AP Soraka in Twisted Treeline.

replies.body: This should be fixed in the next patch :)
Had this happen to my roommate, also on TT. May be map specific. He was playing ~~Brand~~ Darius, and he was simply farming, no champs attacking.
